OL,3,CPolice chief defends investigation
OL,4,Cinto Ann Widdecombe's death
OL,6,FA police and crime commissioner has
OL,7,Fdefended her force over the early
OL,8,Fstages of the investigation into the
OL,9,Fmurder of former Conservative minister
OL,10,FAnn Widdecombe amid criticisms it had
OL,11,Fattempted to "massage public opinion".
OL,13,FAlison Hernandez, the PCC for Devon
OL,14,Fand Cornwall, said she was confident
OL,15,Fthe force had "provided a substantial
OL,16,Fand professional response" to the
OL,17,Fmurder.
OL,26,@sD@NOUsD@eO]wD@OOUxD@ZO]
