CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1784058473
OL,3,CPolice chief defends investigation
OL,4,Cinto Ann Widdecombe's death
OL,6,FCounter-terrorism policing is now
OL,7,Fleading the investigation after new
OL,8,Finformation came to light, despite the
OL,9,FDevon and Cornwall force initially
OL,10,Fsaying it was "open minded" about a
OL,11,Fpotential motive but there was nothing
OL,12,Fto suggest it was political.
OL,14,FMore widely, Devon and Cornwall Police
OL,15,Fwarned the public against engaging in
OL,16,Fand sharing speculation online, in
OL,17,Fparticular regarding the motive.
OL,19,FNigel Farage faced calls for restraint
OL,20,Fat the weekend after sharing his
OL,21,Fthoughts about the case.
OL,26,@rD@OOUrD@[O]
