OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1784058473
OL,3,CPolice chief defends investigation
OL,4,Cinto Ann Widdecombe's death
OL,6,FOn Monday Gawain Towler, a senior
OL,7,FReform UK member, said police had
OL,8,Fattempted to "massage public opinion".
OL,10,F"By appearing to rule something out
OL,11,Fand then a few days later bringing it
OL,12,Fback in, they look manipulative and
OL,13,Fthat's a shame," he added.
OL,15,FMiss Widdecombe, 78, latterly a Reform
OL,16,FUK spokeswoman and Brexit Party MEP,
OL,17,Fwas found dead at her home in Haytor
OL,18,Fon Dartmoor, Devon last Thursday.
OL,20,FShe had sustained serious injuries.
OL,26,@pD@NOUpD@eO]rD@AOUuD@PO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
