CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1784058473
OL,3,CPolice chief defends investigation
OL,4,Cinto Ann Widdecombe's death
OL,6,FA 28-year-old white British man who
OL,7,Fwas arrested on suspicion of her
OL,8,Fmurder on Saturday has since been
OL,9,Frearrested on suspicion of the
OL,10,Fcommission, preparation or instigation
OL,11,Fof acts of terrorism.
OL,13,FMs Hernandez said she had spoken with
OL,14,FLaurence Taylor, the head of UK
OL,15,Fcounter-terror policing, to "seek the
OL,16,Freassurance that there has been a
OL,17,Fsmooth handover of the investigation".
OL,26,@wD@]OUyD@eO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
