OL,3,CPolice chief defends investigation
OL,4,Cinto Ann Widdecombe's death
OL,6,FPolice believe Miss Widdecombe was
OL,7,Fattacked on Wednesday last week at
OL,8,Fabout 12.30pm, shortly before she had
OL,9,Fbeen due on Channel 5's Matt Allwright
OL,10,Fshow
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
